unicef-hivaidsic19.def: Percentage of adolescents aged 15-19 who had more than one sexual partner in the past 12 months reporting the use of a condom during their last sexual intercourse.
unicef-hivaidsic19.name: Condom use among adolescents age 15-19 with multiple partners
